event.title: Monthly FSFE Meeting in Zürich, Switzerland

body.p: Monthly FSFE Fellowhsip meeting in Zürich. For the time and place please see the event page. Main topic to discuss: organisation of xcon. New guests are welcome! In case it is your first time at the meeting, please notify about this on the mailinglist: https://lists.fsfe.org/mailman/listinfo/zurich
